[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     94[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mRace and ethnicity data has different governance from PHI in some regulatory regimes; some state insurance and pharmacy laws restrict secondary use of race and ethnicity data more tightly than HIPAA restricts PHI per se. Provider-demographic data (for the override-pattern bias monitoring the recipe explicitly names) has its own governance considerations under HR confidentiality rules and may not be available outside the credentialing or HR system. The recipe's framing-level treatment is correct; the architectural backstop that operationalizes it is missing.[K
