[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    166[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m3[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mPer-suppression-event audit records are not specified.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m When the inference path encounters a suppressed record, the audit record should capture: which patient was suppressed, which canonical hash was being inferred, what action the policy took (excluded the record, suppressed the entire group), what the resulting household-membership state was, and which downstream consumers were notified (or not).[K
