[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    118[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Recipe 5.6 has three review queues (more than any prior recipe in the chapter), each with its own decision context and its own audit needs. The matcher's accuracy depends on the review queues' quality; reviewers' decisions mutate the linkage table or the cross-reference table or the vocabulary store via the same write paths that auto-link uses. Three concrete consequences:[K
